title: What Adjustments Do the Celtics Need to Make? | Weekends with Wos
description:
Wos is joined by The Athletic’s Jay King to discuss what the Celtics did wrong down the stretch of Game 4 and what adjustments can they make moving forward.

Host: Wosny Lambre
Guest: Jay King
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Benjamin Cruz
